
                       Information about application
                       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. General information
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  LCScan is an circuit scanner for static logical network. Interface
connects to paralel port. It has eight TTL level outputs and eight
overload-protected, Schmitt-trigger inputs.
    This is a software, which does not cost money (maybe you must pay
for use Internet). The lope conditions is the acceptance and observance
of the General Public Licence.

OS support: Linux only.
Language support: English and Hungarian.

2. Installer packages
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 a. for Linux
  lcscan-0.3r3-i586.tar.gz          binary package
  lcscan-0.3r3-i586.bin             installer programme

 b. for Windows
  lcscan-0.3r3-win32.zip            binary package
  lcscan-0.3r3-win32.exe            installer programme

 c. source package
  lcscan-0.3r3.tar.gz               source package

3. Settings
~~~~~~~~~~~
   On linux use 'LANG' environment variable to set language of the
   application.

   for example: English:   en_US,
                Hungarian: hu_HU

